<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV36">
<l>tuḻāneṭuñ cūḻiru ḷeṉṟutaṉ taṇṭā ratupeyarā</l>
<l>veḻāneṭu vūḻi yeḻuntavik kālattu mīṅkivaḷō</l>
<l>vaḻāneṭun tuṉpatta ḷeṉṟiraṅ kāramma ṉōvilaṅkaik</l>
<l>kuḻāneṭu māṭa miṭitta pirāṉār koṭumaikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even at this time that has risen as a long aeon, unmoving, not rising,</l>
<l>its cool garland unstirring long surrounding darkness, he does not feel pity:</l> 
<l>“as for her here, she is of unfailing long misery” – alas,</l>
<l>the lord who crushed the longs mansions in flocks on Laṅka. Cruelties.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
